Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.77,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:316100,318770}We're fighting… that?{NOTE:こいつは戦いなんだぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:318770,320150}Let me say it again.{NOTE:もう一度言おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.98,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:320150,321980}Get serious.{NOTE:本気で来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:321980,325030}No, I won't fight a Rider.{NOTE:ライダーはライダーに剣を向けたりしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:325030,326950}There's no point.{NOTE:そんなものは意味がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.16,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:326950,329160}I see.{NOTE:知ってるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:329160,331280}"There's no point", you say?{NOTE:意味なんて何にだってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:39.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:333370,339080}Well, that's your opinion…{NOTE:だが、それがお前らの流儀だっていうなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:339080,340630}…but not ours!{NOTE:合わせてやるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.46,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:340630,342460}As expected from master Gale.{NOTE:さすがゲイル様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.13,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:342460,345130}You're not like the others!{NOTE:他の方々とは一味違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:345130,347720}If we're going to fight, I will be the winner.{NOTE:合わせた上で俺が勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:360270,361770}Whew.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.48,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:361770,363480}What's with that Rathalos?{NOTE:リオレウス同士だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:363480,366820}Not only he can breathe fire, he's equally strong at deflecting it.{NOTE:炎を浴びせ合ってもお互い火には強いからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:10.41,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:366820,370410}Equally strong?{NOTE:お互いリオレウス同士だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.37,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:376410,378370}Equally?{NOTE:お互い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:384750,386210}What's with you?{NOTE:何なのだお前？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:386210,387760}You're creeping me out.{NOTE:感じ悪いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:387760,390640}You're a disgrace to Felynes.{NOTE:アイルーの風上にも置けないな。\\Nhttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:36.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:390640,396390}I mean, sure, Ratha is an ordinary species, and your Rathalos is special.{NOTE:確かにレウスは普通のリオレウスで、お前のとこはリオレウス希少種だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:42.73,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:396390,402730}And you may be stronger, but nothing can beat Lute and Ratha's kinship.{NOTE:モンスターとしての強さは上かもしれないが、リュートとレウスには絆の強さがあるのだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.99,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:406690,409990}Master Gale, he has no clue.{NOTE:ゲイル様。こいつら何も知りません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:410990,412870}You can't blame him.{NOTE:しかたがないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:412870,415040}Why don't we teach him the hard way?{NOTE:なら教えてやるかか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.00,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:415040,417000}Dusk, let's use Thunder Strike.{NOTE:ダスク。龍光まといだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:423460,425090}What's with that glow?{NOTE:何だ、あの光は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.92,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:425090,427920}He just said Thunder Strike.{NOTE:だから「龍光まとい」だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:427920,431470}"Thunder Strike" can be used only by Stygian Zinogres.{NOTE:「龍光まとい」はジンオウガ亜種が使うものだぞ。\\Nhttp://monsterhunter.wikia.com/wiki/Stygian_Zinogre}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:431470,434350}How can a Rathalos use it?{NOTE:何でリオレウスが龍光をまとうのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.93,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:434350,437930}It's because we've awakened its sleeping kinship gene.{NOTE:眠っていた絆遺伝子を目覚めさせたからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:437930,439680}A kinship gene?{NOTE:絆遺伝子?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.23,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:439680,441230}What's that?{NOTE:なんなのだそれは?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.23,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:441230,444230}You don't know anything, do you?{NOTE:お前ら本当に何も知らないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.44,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:444230,446440}Not even about the Rite of Channeling?{NOTE:伝承の儀を知らないんだ。\\Nhttps://game8.jp/mh-stories/91329}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:446440,448650}So what if I don't know!{NOTE:はっきり言って知らない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:448650,449860}Just tell us already!{NOTE:なんだそれは!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:35.41,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:449860,455410}If you awaken the kinship genes, you can increase Monstie's abilities.{NOTE:だから絆遺伝子を目覚めさせて、オトモンの能力を増やすんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:458240,461750}Hey, Rider. Try dodging this Dragon Breath!{NOTE:よ、ライダー君。拡散龍ブレスだ！}
