Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.96,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:467710,469960}A Rathalos can't use such thing.{NOTE:リオレウスはそんなもの使えないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.68,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:469960,472680}Oh, really…?{NOTE:それがそうじゃないんだ。}
