Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:25.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:561010,565890}Then he told Lute to give up his Kinship Stone and challenged him to a battle…{NOTE:それでそいつはリュートに絆石をよこせと言って戦いを挑んできて…}
