Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:35.40,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:691980,695400}Is that supposed to change Ratha?{NOTE:それってレウスを変えちゃうってことなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:695400,698320}For now, we can't know for sure.{NOTE:話を聞いてみないと分からないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:698320,701450}But whatever it is, it won't change our kinship.{NOTE:…俺たちとオトモンの絆は変わらないと思うよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.24,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:704740,706240}Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.49,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:706240,708490}We're pretty small in numbers.{NOTE:これだけの数のライダーがいるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.62,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:708490,710620}Why don't we all go?{NOTE:全員で迎え撃ったらどうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:55.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:710620,715130}Yeah! Let's all kick their butts!{NOTE:そうか！全員でボッコボコにしてやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:59.21,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:715130,719210}But we're not used to fighting other Riders.{NOTE:だけど俺たちライダー同士で戦うのは慣れてないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.51,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:719210,722510}It's different from fighting a monster.{NOTE:モンスター相手とは勝手が違うからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:722510,723590}It is.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:07.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:723590,727680}He pulled out his sword and slashed Ratha while I was still riding.{NOTE:あいつ剣を抜いて俺とレウスに斬りつけてきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.85,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:727680,729850}He went that far?{NOTE:そんなことまでしてくるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.14,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:729850,732140}This is bad.{NOTE:それは良くないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:732140,734600}And it wasn't just him.{NOTE:それに向こうも一人とは限らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:734600,737730}He had a companion like Floof.{NOTE:チャモの絵でも仲間がいるみたいだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.65,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:737730,739650}It's just as Chief Omna says.{NOTE:オムナ村長の言う通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.03,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:739650,742030}We need to hurry and meet the Channeler.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ急ごう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.04,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:747030,749040}Master Gale! Look there!{NOTE:ゲイル様！あそこは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.45,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:749040,750450}We found them.{NOTE:見つけたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.39,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:768810,770390}What is it, Aptonoth?{NOTE:どうした？アプトノス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.85,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:773390,774850}Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.02,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:774850,777020}Somebody's gaining on us.{NOTE:近づいてくるやつがいます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.19,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:777020,779190}They must be…{NOTE:きっと例の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.98,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:779190,780980}Yep, that's an Ebon Rider, for sure!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズでしょう！}
