Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:782490,783780}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.86,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:784860,785860}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
