Comment: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.01,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,{TIME:788016,788016}$Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:790080,791080}Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
