Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.67,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:792500,794670}He must have followed us.{NOTE:追跡してきたんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.13,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:794670,797130}Everyone should go ahead.{NOTE:皆は先を急いで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.76,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:797130,798760}I'll stop him here.{NOTE:ここは俺が食い止めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.26,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:798760,800260}Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:24.47,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:800260,804470}Even if he rides a Rathalos, I can delay him with this flash ball!{NOTE:相手がリオレウスでもこの閃光玉でくらくらさせてやりますよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.97,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:807720,808970}And just who are you?{NOTE:ん？何？お前。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.40,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:812850,816400}I'm a Rider from Hakum. I won't let you pass.{NOTE:ハクム村のライダーだ。ここは通さないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.40,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:816400,818400}Won't let me pass, huh…?{NOTE:通さないって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:818400,821240}Isn't your Monstie an Aptonoth?{NOTE:お前のオトモンそれアプトノスだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.99,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:822530,823990}What of it?{NOTE:見ての通りだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.49,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:823990,827490}An Aptonoth? An Aptonoth against…{NOTE:プトノス？アプトノスで俺の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:827490,830080}…against my Dusk?{NOTE:俺のダスクを止めようっていうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:830080,831500}Are you for real?{NOTE:マジか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.04,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:833040,836040}It's hilarious, Master Gale.{NOTE:これは笑えますね、ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.17,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:837170,839170}What's wrong with my Aptonoth?{NOTE:アプトノスの何がおかしい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:841170,844180}It probably won't be worth much, but…{NOTE:どうせ大したものじゃないだろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:844180,846930}…hand over your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:お前の絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:846930,850680}If you don't make a fuss about it, I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.89,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:850680,851890}Don't underestimate me!{NOTE:なめるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:851890,853690}Let's go, Aptonoth!{NOTE:いくぞアプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.60,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:853690,855600}You're the one who's underestimating.{NOTE:なめてんのはそっちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.48,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:858480,859480}How's that?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.69,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:860820,861690}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.83,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:868620,871830}Why didn't that flash ball work?{NOTE:何で閃光玉が効かないんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:874000,876750}You're clueless, aren't you?{NOTE:お前らホント何も知らないのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:47.30,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:885930,887300}What was that?{NOTE:今の何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.01,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:887300,890010}It must've been that Monstie's Dragon Breath!{NOTE:あのオトモンの拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.35,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,{TIME:890010,891350}Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.31,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:891350,892310}Stone!{NOTE:ストーン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.02,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,{TIME:892310,894020}Go without me!{NOTE:皆は先に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.85,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:894020,896850}Dan, I'll go as well.{NOTE:ダン先輩俺！も行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:901320,903650}What do we do, Dan?{NOTE:どうします？ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.11,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:903650,905110}We hurry up.{NOTE:先を急ぐぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.49,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:905110,909490}No matter what, we need to get you to the Channeler!{NOTE:お前たちを何としても伝承ジイさんの元へ送り届ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:909490,911450}That's our mission!{NOTE:それが俺たちの使命だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.92,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:915080,918920}Master Gale! Two people that aren't Lute are coming!{NOTE:ゲイル様！リュートじゃないやつが二人向かってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:918920,921300}Ha! How persistent!{NOTE:ハッ！懲りもせず！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.63,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:923210,924630}Is he the one?{NOTE:あいつか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:926590,929300}Hand over your Kinship Stones.{NOTE:お前らの絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:929300,932850}If you do as I say, I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.89,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:932850,934890}That's some pretty big talk.{NOTE:でかい口をたたくんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.56,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,{TIME:934890,936560}There's two of us, you know!{NOTE:こっちは二人だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.27,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,{TIME:936560,938270}We'll attack you from both flanks.{NOTE:挟み撃ちにするぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:48.03,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:944280,948030}They really don't know a thing about fighting.{NOTE:こいつらホント戦い慣れしてませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:949030,951200}Honestly…{NOTE:まったくだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:951200,952910}Let's crush them.{NOTE:食らわせてやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:952910,954580}Dragon Breath.{NOTE:拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:06.97,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:963590,966970}After we pass through this cave, we arrive at the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:この洞窟を抜ければタルジュ雪原だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:966970,968970}We can lose him here.{NOTE:何とか逃げ切れそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:971470,973640}Oh no!{NOTE:いいや、駄目だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:973640,975770}He's caught up onto us!{NOTE:追い掛けてきた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.85,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:975770,977850}Hurry up and get in the cave!{NOTE:お前たちは早く洞窟へ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:977850,979270}But what about you?{NOTE:ダン先輩は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.69,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:979270,980690}Leave it to me!{NOTE:ここは任せろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.77,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:980690,981770}Just hurry up and go!{NOTE:早く行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:981770,983110}But…!{NOTE:だけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:983110,984900}Let's go, Lute.{NOTE:行こう、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:984900,987820}Yeah, we need to meet with the Channeler.{NOTE:そうよ。伝承ジイさんに会わないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:33.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:987820,993370}Don't worry! Navirou will guide you through the cave!{NOTE:そうだ！ナビルーのナビに従って洞窟を進むのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:993370,996500}All right then, Dan, we'll see you later.{NOTE:じゃあ、ダン先輩。行ってくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:996500,998290}Be careful!{NOTE:行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.04,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:998290,1000040}Just leave it to me.{NOTE:任せておけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.21,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000960,1002210}Ride On.{NOTE:ライドオン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.50,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003790,1005500}Qurupeco!{NOTE:クルペッコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.59,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010720,1012590}Ah, it's dark!{NOTE:うはっ！暗い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.97,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012590,1014970}I can't navigate like this.{NOTE:これではナビができないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.14,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014970,1017140}Leave it to me here.{NOTE:ここは私に任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.52,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017140,1019520}Kira-kira-nyaa!{NOTE:キラキラニャ〜ン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.48,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020890,1023480}Good work, Fifi.{NOTE:さすがですねティティ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.27,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023480,1025270}Let's go.{NOTE:さあ行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:09.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025270,1029240}It's not Navirou's fault this place is too dark to see!{NOTE:ナビするナビルーの立場がニャ〜い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:19.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034280,1039580}Great, here comes another weakling Rider.{NOTE:おいおい、またいるよ、弱そうなライダーが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.33,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039580,1042330}It's only small fish.{NOTE:身の程知らずばっかりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.50,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044500,1046500}What did you do to my friends?{NOTE:俺の仲間はどうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049340,1051800}They're off licking their wounds somewhere.{NOTE:向こうでみんなのびてるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051800,1054300}You can avoid their fate by giving us your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:絆石さえ奪えば用はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.64,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054300,1056640}Don't screw with me.{NOTE:ふざけるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.14,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056640,1060140}Isn't that a Qurupeco?{NOTE:お前のオトモンクルペッコじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060140,1063850}Think you can stop us with that?{NOTE:それで俺たちを止められるとでも思ってんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.36,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063850,1066360}Don't make fun of my Qurupeco.{NOTE:クルペッコをなめるんじゃないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.94,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067570,1070940}Qurupeco… Qurupeco…{NOTE:クルペッコはな…クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.49,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070940,1073490}Qurupeco is…!{NOTE:クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.37,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081120,1082370}How's that?{NOTE:どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.13,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082370,1085130}Didn't think a Qurupeco could do something like this, did you?{NOTE:クルペッコはこういうことができるんだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:09.51,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085130,1089510}Wah, it just multiplied.{NOTE:うわー、こいつら数だけは揃えましたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089510,1092590}It still doesn't change anything, though.{NOTE:だが、しょせん数だけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.55,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092590,1094550}Attack!{NOTE:行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.06,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098890,1100060}Master Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.68,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1100060,1101680}He…!{NOTE:あいつ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104390,1105900}What?{NOTE:何のまねだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.77,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105900,1107770}You're not getting in here.{NOTE:ここは通さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.99,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117490,1118990}What was that?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118990,1122120}Dan must be fighting him now.{NOTE:ダン先輩があいつと戦ってるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122120,1124160}Let's hurry up.{NOTE:俺たちも急ごう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.58,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124160,1125580}How about that?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.88,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125580,1127880}You won't be able to follow them now.{NOTE:これでもう通れないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127880,1130500}You little…{NOTE:てめえ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.42,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130500,1132420}Now you've done it!{NOTE:やってくれたな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.18,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132420,1135180}And there's more where that came from!{NOTE:まだまだ！これからだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.39,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135180,1137390}In top form!{NOTE:絶好調！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.85,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138850,1142850}How long is this cave anyway?{NOTE:しかしこの洞窟はどこまで続いているんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.69,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142850,1145690}We just keep on walking and walking. It never ends…{NOTE:行けども行けども果てしニャ〜い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.90,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147690,1151900}Yeah, but the Darj Snowfields will be waiting for us at the end.{NOTE:タルジュ雪原に着くことは間違いないんだろうけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155070,1159830}Jeez, you sure gave me a hard time.{NOTE:ったく面倒かけさせやがって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.87,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159830,1162870}Looks like we can't go this way.{NOTE:この先には行けませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.71,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162870,1165710}What should we do, Master Gale?{NOTE:どうします、ゲイル様？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.17,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165710,1168170}Further tracking is impossible.{NOTE:追跡は無理だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168170,1170630}We'll return to the Black Castle.{NOTE:いったんブラックキャッスルに戻るぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.88,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170630,1171880}Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.19,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189100,1192190}Dan's group has returned!{NOTE:ダン先輩たちが戻ってきたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:20:01.16,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196320,1201160}Lute said that special Rathalos was tough, but I didn't think it would be {\i1}that{\i0} tough.{NOTE:リオレウス希少種は強いモンスターと聞いてはいたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.75,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202870,1204750}And that's not all.{NOTE:そればかりではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.29,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207250,1210290}It also has the power of other monsters.{NOTE:他のモンスターの力も備えている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.84,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212290,1214840}That's how it went.{NOTE:そういうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:18.89,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214840,1218890}That is the power of the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:それが伝承の儀の力なんじゃよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:25.10,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218890,1225100}It lets a monster use the abilities of other monsters.{NOTE:あれはモンスターに別のモンスターの能力を使えるようにするんじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.25,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225100,1228250}Can it really do such thing?{NOTE:そんなことができるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:33.82,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228250,1233820}Chief Omna. We were robbed of our Kinship Stones.{NOTE:オムナ村長。俺たち絆石を奪われてしまいました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.71,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236110,1239710}Why are you going that far?{NOTE:やつは何のためにそんなまねを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.83,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239710,1240830}Whew.{NOTE:ハァ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.33,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240830,1243330}Now I can't Ride On.{NOTE:これではライダーを名乗れん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.08,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243330,1245080}In bad form.{NOTE:絶不調。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.92,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246370,1250920}Now we're the only ones in the village that can Ride On.{NOTE:今村でライドオンできるのは僕たち三人だけなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.37,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250920,1253370}This is definitely serious.{NOTE:責任重大になったゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.95,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253370,1255950}Yeah, so we'd better do our best.{NOTE:私たちがしっかりしないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.35,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255950,1258350}Our best-nyaa.{NOTE:しっかりするでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.62,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258350,1260620}Hyoro, Mille.{NOTE:ヒョロ先輩ミル先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:05.26,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260620,1265260}Will me and my Velocidrome be of any use?{NOTE:自分のオトモンドスランポスなんですけど大丈夫っすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.18,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267220,1268180}I don't think so.{NOTE:駄目だと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:13.01,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269810,1273010}Mille! You don't have to be so harsh.{NOTE:ミル、そんなはっきり言わなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.71,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273010,1275710}It's better to be honest in this case.{NOTE:はっきりしといた方がいいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:20.61,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275710,1280610}If those Riders show up, we have to know our chance of winning.{NOTE:もしあいつらが現れたら自分の立ち回りを考えてもらわないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.01,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280610,1282010}I'll still do my best!{NOTE:頑張るっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.14,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282010,1285140}When it comes to that, just leave things to me.{NOTE:まっいざとなったら俺に任せな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.46,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292710,1294460}Master Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィス様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294460,1297310}These are all the Kinship Stones we managed to get.{NOTE:これが今回手に入れた絆石です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297310,1299310}Here they are, sir.{NOTE:これでございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:45.26,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299310,1305260}The Riders they belonged to weren't that big a deal, though.{NOTE:大したやつらじゃありませんでしたが４つあるということでご勘弁を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:50.01,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305260,1310010}We didn't manage to snag Lute's Kinship Stone this time around.{NOTE:リュートってやつの絆石は今回取り損ねてしまいましたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:53.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310010,1313280}But we won't fail next time.{NOTE:次は必ず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:57.53,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313280,1317530}Master Gale, where do you think this Lute guy went?{NOTE:ゲイル様、リュートのやつどこ行っちゃったんでしょうね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329490,1331870}You seem to be behaving.{NOTE:おとなしくしているようだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:16.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331870,1336020}Nuts, make a good meal for this good little girl.{NOTE:ナッツ、この良い子ちゃんにうまいものでも作ってやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:18.90,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336020,1338900}Roger.{NOTE:はい。かしこまりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:22.40,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338900,1342400}A good meal for a good little girl.{NOTE:良い子ちゃんにはうまいものですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:33.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350570,1353100}Oh, it's an exit!{NOTE:おお！出口だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353100,1355770}Finally, the Darj Snowfields!{NOTE:ついにタルジュ雪原だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:38.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355770,1358320}Hurrah! We're here!{NOTE:やった！着いた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:42.07,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359820,1362070}Ah… cold.{NOTE:さ…寒い。}
