Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.24,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366910,1368240}Not really.{NOTE:別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368240,1369330}What about you, Fifi?{NOTE:ティティは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:50.83,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369330,1370830}Hmph!{NOTE:フンッ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:52.41,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370830,1372410}I'll be fine with this.{NOTE:これで大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372410,1374580}I'm so jealous.{NOTE:うらやましい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:57.71,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374580,1377710}Wait, I'll create us a hot mist in a second.{NOTE:待ってて、今ホットミストをかけるから。}
