Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394730,1397130}Navirou thinks it's this way.{NOTE:ナビルーはあっちだと思うぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:18.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397130,1398300}Alright, then this way?{NOTE:じゃあこっちか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:19.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398300,1399550}Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:25.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400610,1405360}Hey! Don't leave Navirou behind!{NOTE:こら！ナビルーを置いていくな！}
